<p>It's pandemonium down in the pit lane among the Alpha Tauri crew as Pierre Gasly parks up his car in front of the P1 sign. This is so wonderful to see, and great for Formula One in what has been a very dominant season for Lewis Hamilton.</p>

<p>Charles Leclerc, who retired earlier in the race, is out to congratulate Gasly.¬†</p>

<p>'So close but yet so far. One more lap, I needed one more lap'.</p>

<p>Sainz tried with all his might but Pierre Gasly kept his cool to clinch his first ever win in Formula One.¬†</p>

<p>He is the first new winner in F1 since Charles Leclerc last year.</p>

<p>'OH MY GOD!! WHAT DID WE JUST DO?! DID WE WIN THE F****** RACE?! WE DID IT AGAIN!!!'</p>

<p>Gasly is so emotional over the team radio as the Alpha Tauri team celebrate rapturously in the pits. An historic win for the Italian team at their home venue.¬†</p>

